officialTitle: Women's Knowledges About Gynaecological Aftercare, Hospitalized in Maternity Service, or Consulting in Policlinic, in University Hospitals of Strasbourg
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* women aged over eighteen years old
* women who are able to read and write French

Exclusion Criteria:

* women aged under eighteen years old
* women who aren't able to read or write French
